data.title: Amazon Web Services (AWS)
data.meta_description: Amazon Web Services offers reliable, scalable, and  inexpensive cloud computing services. Free to join, pay only for what you use.
data.text:
Whether you're looking for compute power, database storage, content delivery, or other functionality, AWS has the services to help you build sophisticated applications with increased flexibility, scalability, and reliability

Explore eight strategic areas to drive value with data and AI, backed by real-world use cases
